    "attributes": {
        "action": "Tougher penalties for not paying child maintenance",
        "additional_details": "CSA don\u2019t get the problem solved and it goes on for years them chasing people. In the USA if you owe child support your drivers licence can be revoked and if you are pulled over you can be arrested.\r\nToo many parents don\u2019t pay. I hear this over and over and feel that something needs to be done.\r\n",
        "background": "We feel the Government needs to bring in tougher rules and penalties to stop parents avoiding paying child support.",
